@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Archived
Archived --> Active : process
Active --> Completed : cancel
Completed --> Closed : reject
Closed --> Processing : review
Closed : entry / log return
Processing --> Shipped : confirm
Active --> Archived : revert
Shipped --> [*]
@enduml